<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>FAQs | MediCheck</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css"> <!-- Your main stylesheet -->
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
  <style>
    /* Basic FAQ Styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }

    .faq-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .faq-item {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .faq-question {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }

    .faq-answer {
      display: none;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
      display: block;
    }
    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
  body {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    padding: 0.9rem;
  }

  .faq-question {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-answer {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
}

/* Mobile phones (max-width: 480px) */
@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
  body {
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    padding: 0.8rem;
  }

  .faq-question {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .faq-answer {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>
  <div class="faq-container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">What is MediCheck?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">MediCheck is a medical diagnostic platform that helps users check symptoms, get treatment suggestions, and find nearby clinics.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">Is MediCheck free to use?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes, MediCheck is completely free for users. You can diagnose symptoms and get recommendations without any charge.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">How accurate are the diagnoses?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">While MediCheck uses intelligent logic to match symptoms, it does not replace professional medical consultation. Always consult a doctor for serious conditions.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">Do I need to create an account?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">Creating an account allows you to save your health records and track previous diagnoses, but you can also use the platform anonymously.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question">How can I find nearby clinics?</div>
      <div class="faq-answer">Use the “Nearby Clinics” link in the navigation bar. We’ll help you find clinics around your current location.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Toggle FAQ answers on click
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(item => {
      item.addEventListener('click', () => {
        item.classList.toggle('active');
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
